","msg":"巴 我都用緊Lactic Acid一開頭好似暗瘡印有淡到 皮膚有滑啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用用下好似開始無乜效 唔知係咪好啲印積得太撚耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊好無轉用水楊酸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T19:51:57.000Z","msg":"Paula BHA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e96455b0b40a8654c20e606bc08d66a92e73a34","tid":1012580,"uid":17534,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T22:43:55.000Z","msg":"The ordinary 啲產品都係好specific 一種acid/vitamin, 自己要做好research 知道每一種有咩效用同埋邊啲可以配黎用邊啲唔可以。我係外國所以有實體鋪頭可以問。我用過/用緊依幾隻：<br />\n- Mandelic acid (AHA) - 比較gentle 既AHA所以覺得冇乜效果<br />\n- Hyaluronic acid - 平又有效既保濕<br />\n- Ascorbic acid 8% (Vitamin C)+ Alpha Arbutin - 覺得啲暗瘡所冇咁明顯，啱啱謝既暗瘡唔會咁易有印，但佢個texture 有啲似油 (oil free formula) 所以夜晚用<br />\n- Alpha Arbutin 2% - 同上，不過朝早用，個texture 冇咁油易吸收<br />\n- Virgin Marula Oil - 如果有甩皮夜晚會用佢唔搽晚霜<br />\n- Niacinamide 10% - 可以輕輕控制面油同減少暗瘡<br />\n- Caffine Solution - 我黑眼圈幾嚴重用左唔覺有改善"},{"pid":"bfac410a6a061af54e805a94830223e0433fd244","tid":1012580,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e96455b0b40a8654c20e606bc08d66a92e73a34","tid":1012580,"uid":17534,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T22:43:55.000Z","msg":"The ordinary 啲產品都係好specific 一種acid/vitamin, 自己要做好research 知道每一種有咩效用同埋邊啲可以配黎用邊啲唔可以。我係外國所以有實體鋪頭可以問。我用過/用緊依幾隻：<br />\n- Mandelic acid (AHA) - 比較gentle 既AHA所以覺得冇乜效果<br />\n- Hyaluronic acid - 平又有效既保濕<br />\n- Ascorbic acid 8% (Vitamin C)+ Alpha Arbutin - 覺得啲暗瘡所冇咁明顯，啱啱謝既暗瘡唔會咁易有印，但佢個texture 有啲似油 (oil free formula) 所以夜晚用<br />\n- Alpha Arbutin 2% - 同上，不過朝早用，個texture 冇咁油易吸收<br />\n- Virgin Marula Oil - 如果有甩皮夜晚會用佢唔搽晚霜<br />\n- Niacinamide 10% - 可以輕輕控制面油同減少暗瘡<br />\n- Caffine Solution - 我黑眼圈幾嚴重用左唔覺有改善"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T23:14:53.000Z","msg":"絲打好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇嚟我都係唔多啱用<br />\n因為用過b5感覺皮膚都麻麻哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83aa97802234d8a60a26fd610b24165c9b84cb8","tid":1012580,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b898a353a05758529eeba064b5794b76f83c7d27","tid":1012580,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T19:28:07.000Z","msg":"巴 我都用緊Lactic Acid一開頭好似暗瘡印有淡到 皮膚有滑啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用用下好似開始無乜效 唔知係咪好啲印積得太撚耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊好無轉用水楊酸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T23:24:28.000Z","msg":"我啲印冇咩淡 淨係多咗暗粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過下巴粉刺見到係少咗同皮膚滑咗啲<br />\n就係咁我先繼續試佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bffd104e48944af4f47fa94bb475195f54b23fe","tid":1012580,"uid":70448,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T23:35:04.000Z","msg":"b3 會同酸性產品打交，官網有講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溝埋一齊用會無效或者刺激皮膚<br />\n<br />\n建議樓主睇睇官網<br />\n有詳細介紹每樣產品同注意事項<br />\n佢啲產品根本係設計俾美容狂熱者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每樣野功效都好明確專注<br />\n所以好多都濃度比較高<br />\n特別係酸類,vitc, retinoid<br />\n<br />\nyoutube都有啲講解得幾好<br />\n睇完官網了解完可以再補充啲基本知識<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LSEsLLrgHsY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLSEsLLrgHsY&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=13cbae8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LSEsLLrgHsY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ePp79a0L8OU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FePp79a0L8OU&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=aef7181e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ePp79a0L8OU</a>"},{"pid":"a056cb23edd60ffbdcff9899888aee0d14ae2d16