28af37a","tid":1012580,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"另外順便報告下（最初講到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n其實我total 有用lactic acid，b3，b5<br />\n最初係b5+acid用一日、b5用兩日咁隔住用<br />\n後尾見到生粒粒就停咗所有產品<br />\n過咗一排粒粒都冇消 所以又手痕用返<br />\n主要acid同b3隔日用 情況冇改變 都係有生粒粒<br />\n噚晚敷完mask決定acid同b3一齊用<br />\n今日起身見到好多粒粒唔見咗 皮膚平滑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係同個mask有關定產品有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純粹分享下自己嘅情況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f23118c8007eda43c263c1345d302c537eb85ac","tid":1012580,"uid":29601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2159cc41a07e10b56a992ed263efe05e6b8420f","tid":1012580,"uid":44080,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b898a353a05758529eeba064b5794b76f83c7d27","tid":1012580,"uid":29601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T19:28:07.000Z","msg":"巴 我都用緊Lactic Acid一開頭好似暗瘡印有淡到 皮膚有滑啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用用下好似開始無乜效 唔知係咪好啲印積得太撚耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗緊好無轉用水楊酸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T19:51:57.000Z","msg":"Paula BHA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T19:45:21.000Z","msg":"睇落好似唔錯 會試試"},{"pid":"a55f45421b5cffac08283cb767012814bea49e3d","tid":1012580,"uid":91094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T22:20:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://建議用新野之前上www.skincarisma.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B0%E9%87%8E%E4%B9%8B%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%8Awww.skincarisma.com&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=a2ede66f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">建議用新野之前上www.skincarisma.com</a> check下件野成份先"},{"pid":"061f7ddbbbce29a12a66eea22448f